This will yield undefined behaviour as the alignment of reqbuf is 1, but the required alignment of `struct pldm_oem_meta_file_io_write_req` is 4.

Instead you can use something like:

```
alignas(struct pldm_oem_meta_file_io_write_req) unsigned char reqbuf[decodereqlen];
```

And from there, instead of `reinterpret_cast<>()`, use placement-new:

```
auto request_msg = new (reqbuf) pldm_oem_meta_file_io_write_req;
```
